summary: An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley between Blocks Three (3) and Four (4), Crown Addition to the City of Seattle, by grading the same and by providing for the necessary surface drainage, in accordance with Resolution No. 2057 of the City Council of the City of Seattle, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle
